Review medical record to have this information. If incomplete information, measure by yourself and report.
Note the weight taken at the time of birth in grams. If birth weight has not been taken, ask health care staff to measure it.

Note: (Touch or stroke the corner of the baby’s mouth. He will move his head towards the stroking)
